---
title: Baked Chermoula Chicken with Carrot Couscous & Roast Veggie Toss
description: Who doesn’t like a bit of char on their chicken? This one gets a generous coating of our punchy chermoula spice blend before
it crisps up in the pan until golden. Finish it off in the oven so you have the most succulent result that pairs beautifully with our veggie-packed couscous.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/baked-chermoula-chicken-8c991180.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/baked-chermoula-chicken-6093707a8fad57137d20664e-426ec603.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/baked-chermoula-chicken-6093707a8fad57137d20664e
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
nutrition:
  fat: 33.3 g
  saturated fat: 10.6 g
